document.topic_text: Barcelona an chak Nilaini zan khan Barcelona-in friendly match-ah Italian club Sampdoria chu 3-1 in an hneh. Catalan club tan hian Luis Suarez-a'n (16') goal hmahruai a khung hnuah Lionel Messi chuan goal hnih (21', 34') dang a khung belh. Inkhel ṭan hman hian Barcelona-in an player thar Denis Suarez, Samuel Umtiti, Lucas Digne leh Andre Gomes te chu Nou Camp-a entu mipui hmaah an tlangzarh. Share this Post
